title: love.
lyrics: Saram sai saram baram sai baram gakjau i yeomwo ni barae go deotchildoe eo ...Bari daeul mankeum gudeojim yeon ...Biroso nae sesangi doe eojwo Naui jageun maeumdo Geu ane jaran naeumdo Bus eojigo gu deojigo No ganaerigo namyeon Geujeseo ya boineun naui yeong won Saram sai sarang modu hamkke moyeo seo yeongwoneul barago Mom maeum mudeonaem yeon Biroso uri ui sesangi wanbyeo kae Sarangeuro Sarangeuro Naui jageun maeumdo Geu ane jaran naeumdo Bus eojigo gu deojigo No ganaerigo namyeon Geujeseo ya boineun naui yeong won
